      • getStoreUUID

        UUID getStoreUUID()
        The UUID identifying the IRawStore for which the record was requested (optional, defaults to the current Journal).

        Note: This parameter is intended for scale-out if there is a need to fetch the root block of a historical journal (versus the live journal).
